# 架构概览

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Presentation["表现层"]
        User([用户])
        Electron[Electron 客户端]
        Frontend[React + Vite 前端]
    end

    subgraph Gateway["网关层"]
        IPC[IPC 通信]
        REST[REST API]
    end

    subgraph Service["服务层"]
        Gin[Gin HTTP]
        Handlers[Handlers]
        Services[业务服务]
    end

    subgraph Infrastructure["基础设施层"]
        GoBackend[Go 后端]
        PythonWorker[Python Worker]
        Prisma[(Prisma ORM)]
        SQLite[(SQLite)]
        SunoAPI[(Suno API)]
    end

    User --> Electron
    Electron --> Frontend
    Frontend --> IPC
    IPC --> GoBackend
    GoBackend --> Gin
    GoBackend --> Services
    Services --> Handlers
    Handlers --> Prisma
    Handlers --> PythonWorker
    Handlers --> SunoAPI
    Prisma --> SQLite
```

## 技术栈

| 层级 | 技术 |
|------|------|
| 桌面 | Electron 28 |
| 前端 | React 18 + Vite 5 |
| 状态 | Zustand 4 |
| 样式 | Tailwind CSS 3 |
| 后端 | Go 1.21 + Gin |
| ORM | Prisma 5 |
| 数据库 | SQLite 3 |
| Python | 音频处理 |
